        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-1bee5d5a-f5cc-4786-b132-490b9c4d1bc6">
                Mr. Driberg
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1bee5d5a-f5cc-4786-b132-490b9c4d1bc6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-08-11/debates/823a72fe-052d-497b-8e0b-3df592bda824/HouseOfCommons(PublicGalleries)#contribution-1bee5d5a-f5cc-4786-b132-490b9c4d1bc6">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is my right hon. Friend aware of the enormous amount of time spent by hon. Members sitting in a queue awaiting tickets for their constituents and others, and will he consult with the authorities of the House to see if there is any way of easing this position?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-1bee5d5a-f5cc-4786-b132-490b9c4d1bc6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-08-11/debates/823a72fe-052d-497b-8e0b-3df592bda824/HouseOfCommons(PublicGalleries)#contribution-1bee5d5a-f5cc-4786-b132-490b9c4d1bc6">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





