<p class="">In view of the enormous crowds that wait patiently outside, would my right hon. Friend consider cutting through tradition and red tape and making available these galleries which lie vacant about 95 per cent. of the time? Could they not be available to the public if not claimed by 4.30 p.m., or some such time?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
